What will the money raised in the concerts against the end of the world be used for?
A facility for the Studeo barrier-free educational center, which we completed in its sixth consecutive year with the civil association Tap in Jedli?k?v ustav.
The students of the school of Jedlykovsky Ustav are regularly visited by teachers with whom they carry out fun and interesting activities.
